{"tid":1464421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各位巴絲不如搞返個向旅客致歉兼真和你飛大行動","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:35:20.000Z","uid":289257,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7400cbade97553136a9bba4192ef7da2abdb80f9","tid":1464421,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"上次塞完稅局大扣分<br />\n第二日即刻有巴絲做返道歉行動<br />\n重畀六七左派暴徒葉國謙嘖嘖稱奇<br />\n都叫做補返唔少飛<br />\n<br />\n今次和你飛變成阻你飛<br />\n加上疑似公安被圍毆一幕<br />\n已經畀人大造文章<br />\n我地惟有止蝕<br />\n如果有巴絲聽日搞返個向旅客致歉大行動<br />\n同埋將運動tune返正為和你飛<br />\n咁就真係功德無量<br />\n<br />\n其實要令機場癱瘓<br />\n只可以靠人多塞爆機場<br />\n任何阻外國人搭飛機都係揠苗助長<br />\n會有反效果<br />\n希望各位巴絲明白<br />\n<br />\n都係個句：<br />\n不割席、不分化<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"fad9522642597316d42d579f219a948018fcd051","tid":1464421,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"文宣組朋友請入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743c5f2abb56b5ea17384f32c51cd1185e8610d4","tid":1464421,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"文宣組都離運動已去了嗎？"},{"pid":"4689c5838c287aebb4acf77647bc40b4efee9187","tid":1464421,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"743c5f2abb56b5ea17384f32c51cd1185e8610d4","tid":1464421,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"文宣組都離運動已去了嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"886d88ee74b0151be807129177a3ac247c8af480","tid":1464421,"uid":235345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e20a94ddc8bcf0d7854f3c2c63da8d000f6d36f0","tid":1464421,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"不分化，不割蓆<br />\n個個行出黎都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n721 811"},{"pid":"bf242ed940c4a05aa77e8a4afe6b